Hi {!Contact.OwnerFirstName}

It has been two weeks since the Grad asked to withdraw from The Challenge Society and no action has been recorded. Please look at {!Contact.Name}'s record and contact them to see if you can change their mind and find a way for them to remain with The Challenge Society. Click on this link to see the record: {!Contact.Link}

If you are able to change their mind, then please remove the date from the 'Date of YPPG withdrawal notification' field.

If you are not able to change their mind, then please put their date of your conversation with them into the 'Withdrawal confirmed by Owner' field, so that it is clear that they are definitely withdrawing. Please also note their reason for withdrawal.

This is a standard email, sent automatically whenever a Grad notifies us that they want to withdraw.
